<l>makaṉ ṟantaik kāṟṟu mutavi yivaṉṟantai</l>
<l>yeṉṉōṟṟāṉ kolleṉuñ col</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The favor a son does his father is the phrase: "This man's father—</l>
<l>what [great] austerity must he have done!"</l>
